    <div align="left" id="post_message_222030">Dispike the fact that I have leveled every arti &quot;the hard way&quot;....&quot;the only way&quot; I would like to see a change like that, or anythign really for the sake of any alts I roll at the least.<br />
<br />
I just had to say theres nothing wrong with raising the use of PC items its when people combine arti+player crafted<br />
<br />
Also mythic is adding in 5+ new abilitys every patch but not giving us any additional slots...<br />
<br />
I remember when you needed 200hits 75dex/str/con/qui cap each resist and thats all you could do as a assassin it was easy....they they threw in melee speed, melee damage, +cap stat Now templates are harder and harder....if in the next expansion they make any new stats that effect RvR it will be impossible to have a template that covers everything without more imbue points or more slots.<br />
Meanwhile crafters from the begining were told &quot;player crafted items will always be better then droped&quot;. I would Challenge anyone here to do a 5point overcharged MP vest with reactive proc that could match gov, seriously it cant be done.</div>
